
<div class="registration-parent">
    <div id="text">
        <div>
            Time is running out!
            <br>
            Every day, we find ourselves checking the clock wishing to have more hours in a day.
            <br>
            Wouldn't things be easier if the day was 25 hours long?
        </div>
        <div>
            So why not make a timeless petition to make our voices heard to the future generations, where all amazing
            <br>
            theories about time will not only be hypotheses in mathematical equations, but will be real!
            
        </div>
